{"tid":1057952,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女神無啦啦unfollow咗我IG 點算？","createTime":"2019-03-12T08:18:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T08:29:28.000Z","uid":198204,"like":12,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0aecc9402d24ea136719fae7a2d86f1c3446a540","tid":1057952,"uid":198204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:18:06.000Z","msg":"事咁的 我今日睇我限時動態睇下有邊個人睇咗啦<br />\n我發現冇咗女神個名 佢平時都會係最快嗰10個睇我限時動態 於是我咪睇下做咩事 點知就比我發現佢unfollow咗我... 雖然平時冇乜點同佢傾計  淨係會同佢講生日快樂 因為我同佢係同一日生日 <br />\n同埋有時喺IG見到佢限時動態同我追同一個星嘅時候會傾兩句  咁我而家應該點做好呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正評 問佢做咩unfollow我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  負評 unfollow返佢"},{"pid":"400d53b06b6c16a4773ef6fc5bc8b2309fdbc47c","tid":1057952,"uid":172244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:18:56.000Z","msg":"快啲做死狗去問返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3ee33a03332adc84faa9f8047afde0ee2ee9d3","tid":1057952,"uid":48631,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:19:46.000Z","msg":"因為佢一開Ig,就忍唔住係咁mon住你幾時post相,覺得好辛苦,所以忍痛unfollow左你"},{"pid":"29003faf3eeed2968a60610ac3bc3ff04b74b923","tid":1057952,"uid":164167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:21:26.000Z","msg":"醒下啦<br />\n一直都無follow過你"},{"pid":"73ed381924df2bf613d57433ddf3ca0d467d2319","tid":1057952,"uid":198204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29003faf3eeed2968a60610ac3bc3ff04b74b923","tid":1057952,"uid":164167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:21:26.000Z","msg":"醒下啦<br />\n一直都無follow過你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"幻覺嚟嘅啫 嚇我唔到嘅"},{"pid":"94041bdab660fdf0e4b1e673097c83709f447cd5","tid":1057952,"uid":172608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:22:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec4b814151847e4e47382d6a7dbd6f5cd3b1e8